{"tid":912794,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 慢煮鹽水雞柳","createTime":"2018-11-23T02:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T12:44:07.000Z","uid":30742,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a99beeacc761217e3c56f54629f1242603201d41","tid":912794,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vc2dtf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vc2dtf.jpg&h=d415a524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BPfGRiPq5JM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBPfGRiPq5JM&d=QaamyzB5xWbHQotOHZxTl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7b03dacd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BPfGRiPq5JM</a><br />\n<br />\n老娘自小跟老妺一個愛吃雞脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一個愛吃雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我不嬲對雞胸、雞柳嗤之以鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、淡茂茂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、痴牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自從入手慢煮棒，上網見好多人話整雞柳相當好吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n我之前試左都係爭dd，都唔係我覺得好食既口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n原來秘密在於『浸。鹽。水』<br />\n唔好睇少佢，原來鹽水可以令雞柳或者雞胸變得juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n而家我常備，做好就放冰箱<br />\n要吃時解凍煎一煎就食得，又方便又好食，仲要唔肥tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/11/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fblog-post.html&d=QaamyzB5xWbHQotOHZxTl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a9c12e71\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/11/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=QaamyzB5xWbHQotOHZxTl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fdd15e57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=QaamyzB5xWbHQotOHZxTl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7e16a420\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=QaamyzB5xWbHQotOHZxTl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=88a91116\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"c0d7c08517c9998a632d39db54f6853e7a491dcf","tid":912794,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f